{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A beautiful, cloudless day on the ocean. The hustle and bustle of the crew's activities ring out in an endless drone. The salt spray on the sundried skin - invigorating. Wait, you're facing the wrong way. Turn around...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An intense storm cloud, almost black with menace, looms above the world. And we're heading straight for it...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We must prepare the ship and ourselves for whatever we find inside.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- A 30-40 minute interactive, mystery-laden story. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Explore a strange pirate ship to find and roll up all the flags and sails. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Interact with oddball denizens, and navigate underwater mazes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Intricately detailed artwork and animation, that will move you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- A collection of weird and wonderful characters, some of which love eating things that aren't food. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Whoa! Some action. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Disturb a parrot, pet a cat. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- An original soundtrack by magicdweedoo, that shifts the fibres of the soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">BEST EXPERIENCED WITHOUT DISTRACTIONS, WITH NOISE-CANCELLING HEADPHONES.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Red Feather","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3187550/b451426595e3a88ce699e889a3ff879eabb74c44.jpg"},{"name":"Music Box","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3187550/8385fd303ab66804b7bae49df4f9fda60b8d1627.jpg"},{"name":"Binoculars","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3187550/ff755fcf4e2a3d4a3b649e6e3de96fea49c74988.jpg"},{"name":"Sec